Hello, can I get an api access token for api integration

To fetch your API Access Token, please log in to the Newsbreak Admanager Platform. Click on Tools - Resources - API Access Tokens. Here you can click 'Generate token' to create your own API access token. Remember, this token is tied to your user ID and should not be shared with anyone else.
is it possible to get an ad duration time higher than one minut

Currently, NewsBreak does not specify a maximum duration for ads, but typically video ads are kept short to maintain viewer engagement. If you have specific requirements or need further clarification, I recommend reaching out to our support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com for more detailed information.
